    {
      "folder": "jZWW6y5VjVRbbU7t",
      "name": "Flight",
      "type": "campaignFeature",
      "effects": [],
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "gm": "",
          "value": "<p>The Wyvern Flight ignores all ground- based difficult terrain and cannot become mired by effects that can be escaped by flight. When they use the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.Pu5bptxLrKFyEzFh]{Disengage} action against armies that can’t fly, their check result is improved one degree. Armies that lack the ability to fly suffer a –2 circumstance penalty on Advance actions against a Wyvern Flight.</p>"
        },
